OL,6,FAs the debate around assisted dying
OL,7,Fgains pace in the UK, a clinic in
OL,8,FSwitzerland has apologised to the
OL,9,Ffamily of a man who took his own life
OL,10,Fwithout them knowing. ITV News UK
OL,11,FEditor Paul Brand reports
OL,13,FA clinic in Switzerland which helps
OL,14,Fhundreds of people to die each year
OL,15,Fhas apologised to the mother of a
OL,16,FBritish man who took his own life
OL,17,Fwithout his family's knowledge.
