OL,6,FFollowing an , Pegasos said it would
OL,7,Fchange its procedures to ensure that
OL,8,Frelatives were always informed in
OL,9,Ffuture.
OL,11,FForty-seven-year-old Alastair Hamilton
OL,12,Ftold his mother he was flying to Paris
OL,13,Flast August, but instead travelled to
OL,14,FBasel where he took a lethal dose of
OL,15,Fdrugs.
