OL,6,FHis family had been supporting him in
OL,7,Fseeking medical help and had no idea
OL,8,Fhe was really travelling to
OL,9,FSwitzerland to end his life.
OL,11,FWhen he failed to return to the UK and
OL,12,Fstopped answering his phone, his
OL,13,Fmother reported him missing.
OL,15,FBank records eventually revealed that
OL,16,Fhe had paid #11,000 to Pegasos to
OL,17,Faccess what's known as a 'voluntary
OL,18,Fassisted death' in Switzerland.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/18
