OL,6,FITV News travelled with his family to
OL,7,Ftrace his final journey and confront
OL,8,Fthe clinic which accepted his online
OL,9,Fapplication form, which has been seen
OL,10,Fby ITV News.
OL,12,FLimited to 300 word answers, Alastair
OL,13,Ftold them that his undiagnosed
OL,14,Fcondition was causing him "pain,
OL,15,Ffatigue and discomfort" which had
OL,16,F"devastated my life".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/18
