OL,6,FHowever, he admitted that "there is no
OL,7,Fcurrent, definitive medical
OL,8,Fexplanation" for his illness and that
OL,9,Fhis family did not know he had decided
OL,10,Fto take his own life.
OL,12,FDespite that, Pegasos accepted his
OL,13,Fapplication and within several days of
OL,14,Farriving in Switzerland he was helped
OL,15,Fto die.
OL,17,FITV News managed to trace his final
OL,18,Fjourney to an industrial estate on the
OL,19,Foutskirts of Basel, where we believe
OL,20,FAlastair died in an office block next
OL,21,Fto an asphalt factory.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/18
