OL,6,FAt the request of his mother and
OL,7,Fbrother Bradley, we took them to see
OL,8,Fthe building, where they were overcome
OL,9,Fwith grief.
OL,11,F"It's not the best place to be for
OL,12,Fyour last view of earth."
OL,14,F"It's even more heart-breaking that
OL,15,Fsomeone could have been with him, but
OL,16,Fthey didn't tell us and he didn't feel
OL,17,Fthat (he could)," Bradley said.
OL,19,FBreaking down in tears, his mother
OL,20,Fsaid: "I keep saying to myself 'oh
OL,21,FAlastair'."
