OL,6,FFollowing Alastair's death, his
OL,7,Fbrothers repeatedly emailed Pegasos
OL,8,Fbut were left waiting for a reply.
OL,10,FEventually, with the involvement of
OL,11,Fpolice and the British embassy, the
OL,12,Fclinic responded, confirming
OL,13,FAlastair's death and returning his
OL,14,Fashes to his family in the post.
OL,16,FWe persuaded a representative from
OL,17,FPegasos to meet with Judith and
OL,18,FBradley in Switzerland to answer their
OL,19,Fquestions.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/18
