OL,6,FAt an anonymous office in central
OL,7,FBasel, we were greeted by Sean
OL,8,FDavison, who had spoken repeatedly to
OL,9,FAlastair before he died.
OL,11,FMr Davison does not work for Pegasos,
OL,12,Fbut for a separate organisation called
OL,13,FExit International, which advocates
OL,14,Ffor the right to an assisted death.
OL,16,FHe was the last person Alastair called
OL,17,Ffrom his death bed.
OL,19,F"He said he had told (his family) but
OL,20,Fthey didn't want to talk about it," Mr
OL,21,FDavison insisted.
