OL,6,F"He said they didn't support him. I
OL,7,Fdidn't know they weren't coming until
OL,8,Fthe very end. I had nothing to do with
OL,9,Fit, I was only his friend.
OL,11,F"He even phoned me from his death bed
OL,12,Fand said 'Sean I'm just so grateful to
OL,13,Fhave had a friend to talk to.'
OL,15,F"I tried (to dissuade him) every time
OL,16,FI spoke to him. I said you're a
OL,17,Fhandsome man, you've got such a life
OL,18,Fahead of you. I really pleaded with
OL,19,Fhim, I would never encourage anybody
OL,20,Fto end their life."
