OL,6,FAfter our interview with Mr Davison,
OL,7,Fwe were then asked to leave before the
OL,8,FPegasos representative entered the
OL,9,Froom to speak to the Hamilton family.
OL,11,FDuring the meeting, the family say the
OL,12,Frepresentative apologised for failings
OL,13,Faround the way Alistair's case was
OL,14,Fhandled.JUnder Swiss law, anyone can
OL,15,Fbe helped to take their own life as
OL,16,Flong as the person assisting them does
OL,17,Fnot have selfish motivations.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/18
