OL,6,FBut the best known clinic - Dignitas -
OL,7,Frequires people to have a terminal
OL,8,Fillness, 'unendurable disability' or
OL,9,F'unbearable pain' to qualify for its
OL,10,Fassistance.
OL,12,FThe representative from Pegasos told
OL,13,Fthe Hamilton family that its
OL,14,Fprocedures would now be brought closer
OL,15,Finto line with guidelines set by the
OL,16,FSwiss Medical Association in 2022,
OL,17,Fwhich say a family should always be
OL,18,Finformed if a relative intends to die.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/18
