OL,6,F"I was robbed of the chance of going
OL,7,Fthere and cuddling him whilst he did
OL,8,Fit, giving him a kiss goodbye all
OL,9,Fbecause these checks and balances
OL,10,Fweren't in place at Pegasos," Bradley
OL,11,Fsays.
OL,13,F"We weren't given that chance to
OL,14,Feither be with him or in my case, drag
OL,15,Fhim home, tooth and nail if I had to,"
OL,16,Fhis mother says.
