OL,6,FResponding to our report, Pegasos
OL,7,Fsaid: "As conveyed by Mr. Habegger
OL,8,Fduring the meeting, we would like to
OL,9,Ftell the family once again that we are
OL,10,Fvery sorry that our communication
OL,11,Fcaused them further distress last year.
OL,13,F"We were not sure how to deal with the
OL,14,Fsituation in terms of communication
OL,15,Fand legally and therefore did not act
OL,16,Fas we would today. We hope that our
OL,17,Fmeeting helped them to understand
OL,18,Fbetter the decision and path of
OL,19,FAlastair.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/18
