OL,6,F"Pegasos has always respected the
OL,7,Fapplicable Swiss law without exception
OL,8,Fand continues to do so... we always
OL,9,Frequire reports from medical
OL,10,Fspecialists. Only based on these
OL,11,Freports, other documents and direct
OL,12,Fcontact with the concerned person, a
OL,13,Fdecision can be taken. "We are
OL,14,Fconscious of our great responsibility.
OL,15,FThis is why, in those rare instances
OL,16,Fwhere we have reason to assume that no
OL,17,Finformation has been provided to close
OL,18,Ffamily by the person seeking voluntary
OL,19,Fassisted death, we will abort the
OL,20,Fprocedure on the spot.
